## 9) API endpoints (Flask)

### Main endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/pbix/upload` | Upload and parse PBIX | `FormData(file)` | Full JSON payload |
| GET | `/api/pbix/context` | Parse PBIX by local path | `pbix_path=...` | Full JSON payload |
| POST | `/api/story/generate` | Story generation stream | JSON `{context, model}` | SSE |
| POST | `/api/dax/generate` | DAX generation stream | JSON `{query, context, model}` (+optional `pbix_context`) | SSE |
| GET | `/api/ollama/models` | List local Ollama models | none | JSON `{models}` |

### Additional routes in backend source

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/` | Legacy dashboard page |
| GET | `/storytelling` | Redirect to UI URL |
| POST | `/analyze` | Legacy form-based analysis |

